These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, chaman, siglo
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, animation
1. the prince-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is the chaman-smoker##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person watching horror movies is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar   | siglo | prince | chaman |
| Movie-Genre    | horror    | animation | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, black, light-blue
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, volleyball
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Color       | black | light-blue | chestnut |
| Sport   | volleyball    | cricket     | biathlon        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, entrepreneur, dancer
House: palace, victorian, craftsman
1. the project-manager is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the palace house##1
3. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Job         | dancer     | entrepreneur | project-manager |
| House   | victorian | palace     | craftsman  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, airplane
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, domino
1. the person driving the snowmobile is the person playing whist##1
2. the person driving the train is the person playing domino##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Transport   | airplane | snowmobile  | train  |
| Game         | bridge  | whist | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, scientist, architect
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, baccarat, chaman
1. the architect is between the journalist and the pall-mall-smoker##2
2. the scientist is in an odd position##4
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job         | journalist   | architect | scientist    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | chaman     | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, manager, scientist
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, russian, australian
1. the analyst is the russian##1
2. the australian is the manager##1
3. the manager is in an odd position##4
4. the scientist is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Job   | manager | scientist | analyst   |
| Nationality   | australian     | nigerian    | russian |

