.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, pilot, designer
There are 3 different nationalities: french, american, german
1. the pilot is on the right of the architect##1
2. the architect is between the german and the designer##2
3. the architect is on the left of the pilot##1
4. the french is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Job   | designer | architect | pilot |
| Nationality           | american         | french         | german |

