House: ranch-style, victorian, cottage
1. the ranch-style house is between the victorian house and the person playing go##2
2. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
3. the victorian house is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Game   | chess | canasta | go |
| House    | victorian    | ranch-style | cottage     |

