.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, family, martial-arts
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, february, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | family  | scientific  |
| Birthday         | january | february | september |

