2. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| House   | gothic-revival    | art-deco      | farmhouse |
| Flower       | amaryllis | daffodil | begonia   |

