.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, frog, bird
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, sports, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Pet   | bird  | pony | frog   |
| Movie-Genre         | sports | time-travel   | disaster |

