2. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
4. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | dannemann | game | baccarat |
| Flower     | dahlia    | aconite  | lily   |

