.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, thriller, drama
City: edinburgh, berlin, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching drama movies is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre         | drama | fantasy   | thriller |
| City   | berlin   | edinburgh | paris      |

