.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, volleyball, biathlon
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
2. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Sport      | cycling | volleyball | biathlon |
| Birthday   | july   | may          | june |

