.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
City: hamburg, venice, berlin
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, whist
1. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| City     | venice  | berlin   | hamburg |
| Game   | whist | billiard | mah-jongg       |

 